'''特別應變隊'''（[[英語|英語]]：Special Reaction Team，簡稱：SRT）是[[美國|美國]][[美國陸軍|陸軍]]、[[美國空軍|空軍]]、[[美國海軍|海軍]]和[[美國海軍陸戰隊|海軍陸戰隊]]各軍種執法單位內部的戰術單位，專門應對在各個軍事設施和軍營裡發生的緊急事件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/library/policy/army/fm/19-10/Ch21.htm |title=FM 19-10 Chptr 21 Special Reaction Team<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2019-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190623085243/https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/library/policy/army/fm/19-10/Ch21.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

該類部隊相當於軍方版本的警察[[特種武器和戰術部隊|特種武器和戰術部隊]]，其隊員均在倫納德伍德堡的[[美國陸軍憲兵隊|美國陸軍憲兵學校]]接受訓練。<ref>[http://www.army.mil/-news/2009/02/13/16912-fort-polk-mps-receive-srt-training-at-shugart-gordon-training-complex/ "Fort Polk MPs receive SRT training at Shugart-Gordon training complex"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.army.mil/-news/2009/02/13/16912-fort-polk-mps-receive-srt-training-at-shugart-gordon-training-complex/ |date=20100214091134 }} www.army.mil</ref><ref>[http://www.wood.army.mil/usamps/usamps_training_courses.htm "Advanced Military Police Courses"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wood.army.mil/usamps/usamps_training_courses.htm |date=20090304180234 }} www.wood.army.mil</ref>

